channel.title: Auto Cache downloader help
channel.description:
So i downloaded this source here http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,644328.0.html and it had a auto cache and the link for the non auto downlader was broken so i decided to give it a try and i'm having some issues.. I went into CacheDownloader.java and saw this line. [code=java]private final int VERSION = 5; // Version of cache private String cacheLink = "https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/21405738/RSPS/DaddyHisPorn.zip"; // Link to cache[/code]
And replaced the link with my cache.. [ same cahce i only changed the background of the client ] So it looks like this
[code=java]private final int VERSION = 5; // Version of cache private String cacheLink = "https://www.dropbox.com/s/4b6iyycmzfzaxlr/DaddyHisPorn.zip?dl=1"; // Link to cache[/code]
I also went into signlink.java and since i kept the name the same it shouldn't need changing but in the end this happened to my client. [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/cYLnnSq.png[/img]
Any help guys? Is there something i missed or done wrong?
